Enum Class TranslationKey

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TranslationKey>
de.dei0.blockprot.bukkit.TranslationKey
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TranslationKey>, Constable
public enum TranslationKey extends Enum<TranslationKey>
A translation key for a single string in a translations_xx.yml file. Double underscores are replaced with dots when querying for YAML keys.
Since:
0.1.10
